name: Pleasure Island
description:
“Hi diddle dee-dee! It's Pleasure Isle
for me! Where every day is a holiday
and kids have nothing to do but play”
Honest John, Pinocchio (1940) Part
surreal, indulgent, anachronistic
cyberpunk fever dream, part
cautionary tale, this piece came
together as a result of wrestling with
my inner unconscious child over the
course of four long weeks.
